#40900
Sabotage the First Order~
sabotage~
   The First Order thinks it can march into Black Spire Outpost and cow us
into silence.  I aim to prove them wrong.  Thin out their patrols -- take
down five of their stormtroopers -- and the people here will see that the
occupiers can bleed.  Do this, and the Resistance won't forget it.
~
   Five troopers down.  You fight like someone the Resistance could use.
Take this medpac -- and my thanks.
~
You slip back into the crowd, the mission unfinished.
~
