#40901
A Lightsaber of Your Own~
lightsaber~
   So you wish to carry a lightsaber.  A blade is not given; it is earned.
There is a Weequay bounty hunter stalking Black Spire who has spilled more
innocent blood than I care to count.  Face that hunter and prevail, and you
will have proven the discipline a saber demands.  Then I will help you build
your own.
~
   The hunter is dead, and you still stand.  You are ready.  Take this blade,
assembled around a kyber crystal chosen for you.  May it serve the light.
~
You are not yet ready to walk this path.
~
