#40902
The Collector's Vengeance~
vengeance~
   Oga Garra.  That gangster's thugs raided my den and made off with an
artifact older than the Republic itself.  Oga rules the cantina and thinks
herself untouchable.  Prove her wrong.  End her, and I will reward you from
the deepest vault in my collection.
~
   Oga Garra will steal from Dok-Ondar no more.  As promised -- an ancient
Jedi holocron, one of the rarest treasures in the galaxy.  Guard it well.
~
You have chosen not to cross Oga Garra.  Wise, perhaps.  But no reward.
~
